{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_18021.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303001,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameNarration":"相野未都","narration":"我们能这样相识，@也算是有某种缘分……","narrationBg":"bg_adv_18021.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"在我们提出要帮这位花店老板……@[textRed:春名木乃美]后……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301301}],"nameRight":"伊吹丽良","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"我们是不是帮不上忙……？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303001,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"春名木乃美","textLeft":"不会！@谢谢你们！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303001}],"textLeft":"我很感激你们的好意……@你们真是善良的女孩子……！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301501,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"相野未都","textRight":"遇到困难要互相帮助！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301501}],"textRight":"我们也是这样想的！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303001,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"这样啊……@很棒呢！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"伊吹丽良","textRight":"不，也没有……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303001,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"那么我就恭敬不如从命，@麻烦你们了！"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101101,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameNarration":"相野未都","narration":"于是，我们开始在店里帮忙！@我们需要干的活仅仅是@『按木乃美的吩咐做事！』","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"清佳在后方干活，@我和丽良负责接待客人！@遇到搞不定的事就找木乃美！"},{"narration":"就这样，@我们磕磕绊绊地干起了活……"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story09","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101101,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"秋野枫","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"久等啦！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"夏目佳子","textRigh